{"word":"Beth-Shean","slug":"beth-shean","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Beth-Shean</b> <a href=\"#/H1052\">H1052</a> <br/> A city of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=29'>1Ch 7:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=11'>Jos 17:11</a><br/> Not subdued<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=27'>Jdg 1:27</a><br/> - Bodies of Saul and his sons exposed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=10'>1Sa 31:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=12'>1Sa 31:12</a> <br/> - Called Beth-Shan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=10'>1Sa 31:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=12'>1Sa 31:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=12'>2Sa 21:12</a> <br/> - District of, under tribute to Solomon's commissariat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=12'>1Ki 4:12</a> "}]}